FinancialAccountAddress.name: FinancialAccountAddress
FinancialAccountAddress.description: Represents an address related to a financial account.

ActiveFromDate.description: The date from when the address is active for the financial account.

ActiveToDate.description: The date from when the address stops being active for the financial account.

Address.description: The address related to a financial account.

City.description: The city related to a financial account’s address.

Country.description: The country related to a financial account’s address.

FinancialAccountId.description: The financial account related to an address.

GeocodeAccuracy.description: The level of accuracy of a location’s geographical coordinates compared with its physical address. A geocoding service typically provides this value based on the milestone location’s latitude and longitude coordinates.

LastReferencedDate.description: The most recent date when a user referenced this record.

LastViewedDate.description: The most recent date when a user viewed this record.

Latitude.description: The latitude related to a financial account’s address.

Longitude.description: The longitude related to a financial account’s address.

PostalCode.description: The postal code related to a financial account’s address.

SourceSystemIdentifier.description: The unique identifier of this record in an external system.

State.description: The state related to a financial account’s address.

Street.description: The street related to a financial account’s address.

Type.description: Specifies the address type of the financial account.
